The paper deals with the problem of finding robust patient transfer policies using machine learning to predict patient deterioration. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of a Markov Decision Process model to capture the evolution of patient health suggests that the paper may also belong to the Control Engineering (cs.CE) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the focus on improving overall patient care suggests that the paper may also belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
